OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fwill clear eastwards during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Then mainly dry with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells in the afternoon but a
OL,9,Ffew showers will spread into the far
OL,10,Fwest. Breezy across Kintyre and the
OL,11,FIsles.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMainly dry start but cloud
OL,14,Fand showery rain in the west will move
OL,15,Feast across all parts. Becoming dry
OL,16,Fwith clear spells after midnight with
OL,17,Fpatchy frost inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
