OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cold start to the day with
OL,6,Fa frost for some places. It will
OL,7,Fremain dry with plenty of sunshine but
OL,8,Fperhaps some high cloud spreading east
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and bright on Wednesday but
OL,13,Fcloudier with outbreaks of rain later.
OL,14,FRain bands moving east followed by
OL,15,Fdrier and brighter spells for the rest
OL,16,Fof the week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
